    "content": "This example demonstrates the cache maintenance operation by cleaning and invalidating the cache for the DMA buffers located in the cacheable SRAM region. ",
    "url": "http://localhost:4000/csp_apps_pic32mz_da/apps/cache/cache_maintenance/readme.html#cache-maintenance-operations",
